DESCRIPTION
    Tower of Disasters

SYNOPSIS
    ./my_rpg [OPTIONS]

OPTIONS
    -h                  display the help

KEY INPUT
    In Game:

        `ESC`           Pause the game and open the menu
        `z`             Move forward
        `q`             Move to the left
        `s`             Move Backward
        `d`             Move to the right
        `f`             enable / disable fps counter

    In Settings:

        `ESC`           Go back to the menu

EXIT STATUS
    0                   Successful program execution,
    1                   Usage, syntax or file error.

